text: Louis Rathke (July 8, 1883 - December 24, 1967) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1967 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milwaukee
